item.description:
Hi Incubators!

We have been having a ton of fun so let's continue and welcome in the spring while we are at it.

That's right it's time for an outdoor incubator again. This time we'll be in Cambridge Common to enjoy the grass and the weather. Also bring some props maybe a frisbee or something, Frisprov sounds like a great idea haha. Athletic and brain athletic, lol. Dont worry nobody's required to do it haha.

Cambridge Common is right in Harvard Square so if you look on the map provided by meetup, we'll meet across the street from this point actually in the cambridge common, there are stone walls and such there. From there we won't move far so feel free to come by anytime.

And if you get lost or in need of direction in general, lol give me a call at 617-869-1551.

Any questions?

Lots of announcements this week to so please drop by. Tons of awesome improv events coming up.

Cheers!

Jason
item.name: Before Improvset!!! This weeks incubator!
